  title VR Travel Experts
header.bgImagePackages
  // Used to change the background image in CSS
  .mainArea
    .topCell
      img(src='images/vr.png' height='100' alt='Welcome to VR Travel Experts')
      h1.companyname
        i Welcome
        |  to VR Travel Experts
    .navBar
      ul
        li
          a(href='index.html') MAIN
        li
          a(href='/index_packages') PACKAGES
        li
          a(href='/contact_agents') CONTACT
        li
          a(href='register.html') REGISTER
        li
          a(href='about.html') ABOUT
    .mainCell
      p.byline
        | Envision taking a Safari through the Serengeti National Park without leaving home. VR Travel packages start as low as $25 USD for tours of famous destinations in over 24 countries.

    // Displays the list of agents in the travelexperts MySQL db
